# Model

```scalascript
case class Todo(id: Int, text: String, done: Boolean) derives RowCodec
```

# Schema

```sql
CREATE TABLE todos (id INT PRIMARY KEY, text VARCHAR(120), done BOOLEAN)
```

# Missing column

```scalascript
Db.insert("default", "todos", Todo(1, "missing done", false))
val rows = Db.query[Todo]("default", "SELECT id, text FROM todos", [])
println(rows)
```
